{"type":"system","subtype":"task_notification","task_id":"aa533f1a676716ad5","tool_use_id":"toolu_016fLr5R1XUSLwEmBUfi2ULE","status":"completed","output_file":"","summary":"Explore index.ts and db types","usage":{"total_tokens":32481,"tool_uses":2,"duration_ms":10308},"uuid":"7752a04c-2fe5-4863-856c-139f0ba99922","session_id":"f9901d53-ab05-422c-a65b-76ea18fa6c39"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016fLr5R1XUSLwEmBUfi2ULE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here's what I found:\n\n## App Architecture (index.ts)\n\nThe app is wired as a **Hono-based HTTP server** with several key components:\n\n1. **Database Layer**\n   - PostgreSQL connection pool (`postgres`) shared across all services\n   - Two database clients: `db` (game data) and `authDb` (auth data)\n\n2. **Core Infrastructure**\n   - Solana connection with optional WebSocket endpoint\n   - JWT auth middleware and rate limiting\n   - CORS enabled (no cookies, bearer-token auth only)\n\n3. **Main Services**\n   - Settlement worker: polls for rounds ready to settle\n   - PDA watcher: WebSocket-based instant join/settlement detection\n   - Close Call clock worker: creates rounds on minute boundaries\n   - Event queue worker: async event processing\n\n4. **API Routes**\n   - `/auth` — JWT challenge-response (no middleware)\n   - `/fairness/coinflip` & `/fairness/lord` — games with settlement\n   - `/closecall` — price-oracle betting\n   - `/profile`, `/referral`, `/public-profile` — user data\n   - `/price` — SOL/USD public endpoint\n\n---\n\n## Db Interface (db.ts - first 100 lines)\n\nKey types exported:\n\n**Core Data Types:**\n- `RoundPhase`: \"created\" → \"locked\" → \"settling\" → \"settled\" (or \"expired\")\n- `Round` — Coinflip/Jackpot match with: pda, game, creator, secret, commitment, amount_lamports, phase, match_id, target_slot, result_hash, result_side, winner, settle_tx, settle_attempts\n\n**Close Call Types:**\n- `CloseCallPhase`: \"open\" | \"settled\" | \"refunded\"\n- `CloseCallOutcome`: \"pending\" | \"green\" | \"red\" | \"refund\"\n- `CloseCallRound` — Has pool tracking, price (open/close), entries array, fee\n\n**Events:**\n- `OperatorEvent` — Audit log: id, pda, event_type, payload, created_at\n- `OperatorEventType` — \"secret_generated\", \"tx_built\", \"match_detected\", \"settle_submitted\", \"settle_confirmed\", \"settle_failed\", \"settle_retried\", \"timeout_detected\"\n\n**Insert Params:**\n- `InsertRoundParams` — Constructor for creating rounds\n- `InsertCloseCallRoundParams` — roundId, pda, serverKey, openPrice, openPriceExpo\n\nAll amounts stored in **lamports** (no SOL conversion at DB layer)."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f9901d53-ab05-422c-a65b-76ea18fa6c39","uuid":"2175ee89-bdd7-4daa-b992-cdb07a9c4584","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:32:57.446Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files and report their contents:\n1. /workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/index.ts\n2. /workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts (just the first 100 lines to see the interface/types)\n\nI need to understand how the app is wired together and what the Db interface looks like.","agentId":"aa533f1a676716ad5","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here's what I found:\n\n## App Architecture (index.ts)\n\nThe app is wired as a **Hono-based HTTP server** with several key components:\n\n1. **Database Layer**\n   - PostgreSQL connection pool (`postgres`) shared across all services\n   - Two database clients: `db` (game data) and `authDb` (auth data)\n\n2. **Core Infrastructure**\n   - Solana connection with optional WebSocket endpoint\n   - JWT auth middleware and rate limiting\n   - CORS enabled (no cookies, bearer-token auth only)\n\n3. **Main Services**\n   - Settlement worker: polls for rounds ready to settle\n   - PDA watcher: WebSocket-based instant join/settlement detection\n   - Close Call clock worker: creates rounds on minute boundaries\n   - Event queue worker: async event processing\n\n4. **API Routes**\n   - `/auth` — JWT challenge-response (no middleware)\n   - `/fairness/coinflip` & `/fairness/lord` — games with settlement\n   - `/closecall` — price-oracle betting\n   - `/profile`, `/referral`, `/public-profile` — user data\n   - `/price` — SOL/USD public endpoint\n\n---\n\n## Db Interface (db.ts - first 100 lines)\n\nKey types exported:\n\n**Core Data Types:**\n- `RoundPhase`: \"created\" → \"locked\" → \"settling\" → \"settled\" (or \"expired\")\n- `Round` — Coinflip/Jackpot match with: pda, game, creator, secret, commitment, amount_lamports, phase, match_id, target_slot, result_hash, result_side, winner, settle_tx, settle_attempts\n\n**Close Call Types:**\n- `CloseCallPhase`: \"open\" | \"settled\" | \"refunded\"\n- `CloseCallOutcome`: \"pending\" | \"green\" | \"red\" | \"refund\"\n- `CloseCallRound` — Has pool tracking, price (open/close), entries array, fee\n\n**Events:**\n- `OperatorEvent` — Audit log: id, pda, event_type, payload, created_at\n- `OperatorEventType` — \"secret_generated\", \"tx_built\", \"match_detected\", \"settle_submitted\", \"settle_confirmed\", \"settle_failed\", \"settle_retried\", \"timeout_detected\"\n\n**Insert Params:**\n- `InsertRoundParams` — Constructor for creating rounds\n- `InsertCloseCallRoundParams` — roundId, pda, serverKey, openPrice, openPriceExpo\n\nAll amounts stored in **lamports** (no SOL conversion at DB layer)."}],"totalDurationMs":10312,"totalTokens":33093,"totalToolUseCount":2,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6762,"cache_read_input_tokens":25702,"output_tokens":622,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6762},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
